ng-12: Label nodegroup nodes

With this change each node will be labeled with the following:
* --node-labels=magnum.openstack.org/role=${NODEGROUP_ROLE}
* --node-labels=magnum.openstack.org/nodegroup=${NODEGROUP_NAME}

